Plan[]

  • Prefer usage of "article" or "page" instead of "mod"
  • Change category names to be consistent
  • List changed categories
  • Decide whether to use "material" or "content", in reference to assets of the subject (e.g. song, character), the whole subject (e.g. mod), or anything related to the subject.

Changed categories[]

Categories are changed to introduce consistency.

Notice New category New category
Content Warning Content Warning Pages with content warning
Trigger Warning Trigger Warning Pages with trigger warning
Controversial Controversial Pages with controversy
Spoilers Spoilers Pages with spoilers
Copyrighted Pages with copyrighted assets Pages with copyrighted content
Protected Page none
Large Page Long pages unchanged
Golden Throne Golden Throne unchanged
High Quality Article High quality pages unchanged
On Hold On Hold Mods that are on hold
Discontinued Mod Discontinued Pages with discontinued content
Foreign Language Non-English Mods Pages with foreign language content
Fan Favorite Fan Favorite unchanged
Fan-Made Fan-Made Mods Fan-made mods
Resolved Controversy Mods with resolved controversy Pages with resolved controversy
Unreleased Mod Unreleased Pages with unreleased content
Lost Mod Mods with missing downloads, Lost mods Pages with lost content
Work In Progress Work in progress mods Pages with work in progress content
Upcoming Content Upcoming Mods Pages with upcoming content
Placeholder Used Has Placeholder Pages with placeholder
Partially Lost Partially Lost Pages with partially lost content
Unavailable Download Mods with missing download Mods without download links
Unfinished Page Unfinished pages and stubs Stubs
Outdated Page Outdated Pages in need of updating
Low File Quality Pages with low quality files Pages with low quality files
Low Image Quality Low Image Quality Pages with low quality images
Proofread Needs proofreading Pages in need of proofreading
Unfinished Song Mods with unfinished/not started songs Pages with unfinished songs
Storage Storage Page Storage pages
Disambiguation Disambugations Disambiguation pages
Bad Low quality pages unchanged
Broken Contents TBA TBA

Previews[]

ATTN: User:Isuckatnamestoo reached out to me to avoid the categories appearing on this page. Adjustments have been made on the new notices, making it possible to transclude it without putting in on the category. However, old notices won't be edited, so I decided to stop transcluding it altogether. You can see the version of this page with the old notices on my website (last updated: 10 September 2022).
